    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Manages self-signed certificates for WebTransport

Per libp2p spec:
- Certificates are self-signed
- Validity period ≤ 14 days
- Cannot use RSA keys
- Certificate hashes are advertised in multiaddr
</verbatim> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
